Class CSVDataSource

    Direct Known Subclasses:
    TemporalCSVDataSource

    public class CSVDataSource
extends CSVBase
implements DataSource
    A graph data source for CSV files.

    The datasource expects files separated by vertices and edges, e.g. in the following directory structure:

    csvRoot |- vertices.csv # all vertex data |- edges.csv # all edge data |- graphs.csv # all graph head data |- metadata.csv # Meta data for all data contained in the graph

        Create a graph collection from CSV lines using CSVLineToElement mapper functions.
        Type Parameters:
        G - The graph head type.
        V - The vertex type.
        E - The edge type.
        LG - The graph type.
        GC - The graph collection type.
        Parameters:
        csvToGraphHead - A function mapping a CSV line to a graph head.
        csvToVertex - A function mapping a CSV line to a vertex.
        csvToEdge - A function mapping a CSV line to an edge.
        collectionFactory - A factory used to create the final graph collection.
        Returns:
        A graph collection representing the graph data stored as CSV.
